                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/15640.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Simpich</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Nogales</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-08-04T14:00:00-07:23">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 4, 1915—2 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Attack on Maytorena’s outposts about Nogales has just begun. I saw Maytorena and
                    delivered usual warning as to firing across line. He says he has taken offensive
                    with artillery and can repel Carrancistas.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Simpich.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
